The paper deals with object detection using deep convolutional neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses improvements in training and acceleration of detection, which are relevant to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the use of CNNs is a common technique in neural networks (cs.NE) and the paper deals with image understanding, which is a topic in multimedia (cs.MM).
